    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into wedges</p><p>Cut your<strong> cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Top, tail and grate your<strong> carrot[s] </strong>(no need to peel!)</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
