      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon[s] </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Give it a good mix up until it's smooth – this is your <strong>lemony dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
