      "instruction": "<p>Combine the salad with the <strong>lemony dressing</strong> and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>crunchy pitta salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>shredded harissa free range chicken</strong> over the<strong> crunchy pitta salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the<strong> lemony dressing</strong> and garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped mint </strong>and<strong> dill</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
